|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1ct | [G-VS2 $3,230](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29090690?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | D-VVS1 ~$1,300–$1,500 | ~$1,730–$1,930 | ~53–60% |
