| 2ct | [G-VS2 $16,490](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29307739?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | [D-VVS1 $2,810](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28629934?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $13,680 | 83% |
| 3ct | [G-VS2 $48,780](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/24964101?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | [E-VVS1 $5,800](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28944023?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $42,980 | 88% |

**Note:** lab-grown pricing is intentionally compared at D-VVS1/E-VVS1 because lab-grown D color and VVS clarity are available at the same price that buys G-VS2 in natural. The comparison shows what the Origin Tax actually buys — not just origin, but lower grades too.

